sources.name: registry errors
sources.query: align(1m, last, ts("kubernetes.daemonset.ready", daemonset="*fluent-bit*" and cluster="${cluster_name}"))

sources.name: Pods not Ready
sources.query: align(1m, last,  ts("kubernetes.daemonset.ready", daemonset="*fluent-bit*" and cluster="${cluster_name}")/ts("kubernetes.daemonset.desired_scheduled", daemonset="*fluent-bit*" and cluster="${cluster_name}")*100)
